Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf agreed to be Darky’s apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to prevent Darky and the goats
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from seeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the situation went haywire,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and Darky and the goats still ran into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, Werewolf had no choice but to take Darky away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We only failed to catch him because of Wolffy’s operating mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it’s not like he did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Wolffy has been acting very strangely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he be sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are friends, so go check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad made them himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not supposed to eat that much at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so good to eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what exactly happened yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,after Werewolf took Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}Dad, yesterday—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,1070)}By the way, Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you haven’t really befriended goats, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I haven’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning on going goat-hunting after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, are you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it’s Weslie and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids in the area are always doorbell-ditching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve been acting strangely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m perfectly healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}If there’s nothing else—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,938)}Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s calling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s Wolnie calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie’s voice has been a little gravelly lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where is my razor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s always using my shaver to cut her fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Weslie, you’re here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s my shaver?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the shaver should be somewhere in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let Dad and the goats run into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll have to find someone to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go get my toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Wilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Wilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,…That’s it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries, I’m great at acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just that Wilie…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie, how about we play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide-and-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We play hide-and-seek all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I always win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s different this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You only win if you don’t let Grandpa get caught by the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t your breakfast. Don’t eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how many people are in Wolffy’s family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and Wilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there four plates on the table, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there an extra plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s Wolffy’s cousin’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was coming to visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the last minute, didn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come help me find my toy car, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, why’d you jumpscare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve been acting very strangely lately, Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t keep them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come with me, and you’ll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Goats’ wool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is goats’ wool doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the wool on my goats’ wool coat falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be some low-quality wool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I catch some goats,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll use their wool to make you a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s go outside and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this plant have to do with your recent strange behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has {\i1}everything{\i0} to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought dandelion seeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but chamomile is what sprouted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how can I not be upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just like how I wanted to buy a mango cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was given a durian cake instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you, Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I just bought these new curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re… They’re nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The curtains over here are new, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t Wilie go to get his toy car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s taking him so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie, I’m very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go inside and rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We can play later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie must have gone outside to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The light must be broken. I’ll go fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go. It just tripped, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, why has the light turned off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll see if it’s fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the light is broken for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that person just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cover is about to get blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With the curtains open,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys can see more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See? There’s no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we really just mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be that you guys are too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can visit another day, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is wrong with Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember what I said last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time, you said that I’ve got a tall stature,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice face, and a kind smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You admired me, and you wanted me to be your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant what I said on the airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who I am doesn’t matter. What matters is:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,do you now believe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that your son has truly befriended goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those you saw just now were, in fact, that group of goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats have already come to your house to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still not believe that Wolffy is friends with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m still worried about Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go back to check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, we can eat breakfast in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m still a little worried about you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine, really. I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,—Our cousin!　—Our uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Our uncle’s son. He’s our cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t he say he wasn’t coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wouldn’t, but he ended up coming, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t let them find out your true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m Wolffy’s cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad wants to befriend goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I swear—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe it now, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son has befriended goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m very curious as to how you got in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that, for the sake of your son’s journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to collaborate to catch the goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s do it.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
